+ "Lower"		Lower
+ "" Nop
+ "StaysOnTop"          Pick (CirculateHit) Layer 0 6
+ "StaysPut"            Pick (CirculateHit) Layer 0 4
+ "StaysOnBottom"       Pick (CirculateHit) Layer 0 2
+ "" Nop
+ "Identify"            Module FvwmIdent

DestroyMenu MenuIconOps
